data.description: 5.1% INTEREST RATE! Assumable Loan is the same amount as your 20% down at a 5.1% rate!!! This would also make a great Airbnb or rental property! Historic charm & modern luxury in this renovated 3+ story in Benton Park. 9 ft ceilings, separate living & dining room, open eat-in gourmet kitchen, 2 primary bedroom suites, finished basement, main floor laundry, private parking, a backyard oasis. Fully integrated Smart-home w high-end appliances, designer lighting & luxe touches like surround sound throughout. 2nd floor offers 2 en-suite bathrooms & ample closet space. Several bonus space options for sleep, office, nursery, gym, media room. ‘21 Fenced backyard w enclosed double parking, smart garage-port EV charging capable, ‘21 new siding & impeccable landscaping, front & back round out this rare gated property. Home was gutted in '15, all newer systems. Many updates to interior & exterior in ‘21-‘22.  Newer Outdoor furniture can stay with the house!
